a2a89f6229","tid":1496843,"uid":134178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T16:54:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ac7d92e4b24b6a5ba9926410d157d81247abb1db","tid":1496843,"uid":277263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T16:55:39.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n眼前既香港有幾恐怖？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1478109\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1478109</a>"},{"pid":"9f118759b1b29867fa62117b5fda46f3bdd6ed6a","tid":1496843,"uid":261627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"924b000222f6b8685c73537f5347196df6ea9b5f","tid":1496843,"uid":195832,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T16:54:00.000Z","msg":"其實我好辛苦㗎，<br />\n由開始搞份聯署，呢幾日不斷手動更新名單，<br />\n之後仲要經營個ig page，要瘋狂direct人叫人簽聯署，<br />\n仲要有好多同學仔問我關於罷課詳情又要逐一解釋，<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果咁好彩有同學發現到我係同佢係同一間學校，唔洗話幫我傳開佢，我淨係想見到你幫我叫多人簽份罷課聯署咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T16:55:46.000Z","msg":"幫！！！！"},{"pid":"865825ba14fffeab2294d5f46f9333b3fa3827bb","tid":1496843,"uid":195832,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T16:56:13.000Z","msg":"好想見到我間學校啲同學仔幫手簽份聯署<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d609b1eb56bcdd237e1247ab3a514dbee1770825","tid":1496843,"uid":195832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T16:57:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3cc77a3842fa7242f8ffbd7aea40af3fa803470","tid":1496843,"uid":101498,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T16:58:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: pink;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">是日（823星期五）活動<br />\n銀髮族罷買<br />\n會計界遊行<br />\n基督徒集會<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">人鏈</span><br />\n賣港城一日遊</div></span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BXTv9tG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBXTv9tG.png&h=e866629a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">光復香港，時代革命</div></span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18b1850e5d05b296535f854708b00db105988913","tid":1496843,"uid":195832,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"d510e7ab84bffbd66438b401b4a7590f067dde61","tid":1496843,"uid":259244,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T16:52:03.000Z","msg":"P牌仔推唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你地一定要加油<br />\n如果抗爭罷課罷到學業跟唔上<br />\n勝利之後我地班老嘢係煲底同你地補習<br />\n一定要幫你地補到入U<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T17:01:06.000Z","msg":"我已經救唔返了。<br />\n<br />\n小弟升中六，原本成續都係麻麻，諗住喺呢個暑假補習，希望入到U。<br />\n<br />\n但係我自己由6月9開始一直都有出嚟，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，我已經全部心機放晒入去，連一個禮拜都唔知玩唔玩到兩個鐘電腦。<br />\n<br />\n巴打好意我心領了，你幫多啲仲係升f.5 f.4嘅人啦，佢哋仲有得救㗎。"},{"pid":"ce37f65590e5a5a5f6b4eab46c753b0e6feaeb54","tid":1496843,"uid":195832,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T17:02:05.000Z","msg":"生於亂世真係有種責任㗎"},{"pid":"60a20512ccf2047eca9c4b149301852fe919de86","tid":1496843,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T17:03:19.000Z","msg":"Tui"},{"pid":"074f3b30c4b87038cde39d3553faf7ad0834b583","tid":1496843,"uid":268692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"09c31c1fd2c0f76aac1a3b7accaf25d24f5fe88c","tid":1496843,"uid":195832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T16:45:29.000Z","msg":"我諗冇人係鍾意聽廢話，但希望大家特別容許我講一次廢話。<br />\n<br />\n本身都冇話想話打卡，我都係同平時一樣咁參加遊行集會啫，點解要特登喺連登打個卡喎？<br />\n<br />\n但係呢次都算係特別啲嘅集會，因為係特別講明「中學生」，平時我去參加遊行集會係用一個「香港市民」嘅角度出發，所以係同平時唔同啲，今次想用「中學生」呢個角度去講下我對今次嘅集會有咩感受。<br />\n<br />\n今次嘅集會同平時嘅集會最大唔同係在於真係有好多中學生，我唔識用詞語好形容，總知就係好好好多多多啦。<br />\n<br />\n我明嘅，中學生係要面臨Dse嘅壓力，而且又有好多家庭嘅因素令到大家出唔到嚟發聲，我真係明。<br />\n<br />\n講返正題先啦，今次嘅集會去到7點21分嘅時候大家係決定為以死相諫嘅六位義士默哀一分鐘，咁時間一到，周圍啲喇叭都播緊「誰還未覺醒」，大家都用手機開著電筒，用白色光茫去悼念死者，而我亦都唔例外，拎住一張文宣圖片，內容大概係一位失去咗右眼嘅女仔，寫住「香港警察，意圖媒殺」等嘅字體，同樣地開著電筒喺度揮手。<br />\n<br />\n其實由6月9至今，呢個香港係我17年嚟見過最靚嘅香港，好難得身邊嘅人同自己擁有同一樣嘅價值觀，大家雖然唔相識，但係都係有著同一樣嘅目標，可能大家做嘅手法唔一樣，但其實我哋都係香港人，都係同一樣嘅群體，都係同一樣嘅身份，We are the one。<br />\n<br />\n至今有差唔多八百位義士被捕，可能之後仲會清算得越嚟越多，可能我哋只係一個中學生，力量好細，但其實如果我哋一班人嘅話力量就好大。<br />\n<br />\n所以，有啲卡我係一定要打，希望大家可以出一份力，喺9月2日響應三罷，呢啲係我哋中學生嘅能力範圍之內。<br />\n<br />\n就讓我們去為抗爭者抗爭一次，好嗎？<br />\n-----------<br />\n以上內容係我用我哋學校嘅罷課關注組嘅page打㗎，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你哋都可唔可以加入你哋學校嘅關注組啊？如果冇嘅話你可唔可以做開page嗰個去呼籲人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n多你一個真係多好多㗎。<br />\n<br />\n為這世代有未來要及時擦亮眼精<br />\n<br />\n係時候要醒啦咁多位中學生。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T17:04:18.000Z","msg":"幫手推"},{"pid":"5561f3db2b3741e3ee58